title: Lestat's Coffee House
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, American, Fast food, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. 24-hour trendy coffeehouse that offers a vegetarian soup and a vegan chili (call to confirm) plus vegan pastries, tea, soymilk for coffee. Furniture is antique Victorian. Has computers and nightly entertainment in its theater next door. Free Wi-Fi.
